body.description: Our gps tracking set multiple functions of security, tracking, monitoring surveillance, emergency alarms and management in its entirety. Perfect for tracking vehicles, kids, spouses, elderly persons or assets. How to Use: 1. Insert a working GSM standard SIM card into the tracker, then track and map(with Google maps) in real-time over the internet. 2. Monitoring by sending text messages to the tracker 3. Send 000 to connect cell phone with the GPS 4. Send 777 to receive the location via a link to Google Map 5. Send 102 for a link (http://gpsui.net) to download the app and username and password 6. Send 555 to start recording 7.Send 666 to stop recording and switch to sound sensor mode. Under this mode, if the device is surrounded by higher than 40db voice it will call your phone 8. Send 445 to delete recording on TF card 9. Send 444 to reset phone number 10. Send 888 to check the GPS status (battery, signal, and TF card storage, etc) 11.Send 999 to restart the GPS Pay Attention: Please read the manual before use. If you have any questions, please contact us Please use GSM standard mobile SIM card, Mobile SIM card with GPRS internet access function Check if the SIM card is correctly inserted and used, and whether the direction of the card insertion and chip orientation are correct Check if the card is in arrears and if the locator is turned on. If the indicator light is on, the working status of the indicator light can be determined SIM card size requirement: Nano GSM standard SIM recommended: AT&T, T-Mobile SIM card requires balance to connect and use Specification: Color: black Size: about 1.37*0.78*0.55 inch (L*W*H) Material: ABS Antenna type: GSM GPS positioning accuracy: about 100m Battery: 3.7V 300mA lithium battery Battery working time: about 100h Standby time: 12 days . Working time 4-6 days Package included: 1*mini tracker 1*USB cable 1*manual Notes: Charging requires a SIM card to be inserted, SIM card requires a balance, otherwise the device cannot be used normally
